author: Alan Tovey
title: Concorde Mark 2: Airbus files plans for new supersonic jet
text: Engineering Concorde Mark 2: Airbus files plans for new supersonic jet Aerospace giant Airbus sketches out ideas for passenger jet that could fly faster and higher than Concorde in US Patent Office filing Concorde might have gone out of service, but aircraft designers have hopes for a successor to the iconic jet Photo: Dennis Stone / Rex Features By Alan Tovey , Industry Editor 12:23PM BST 04 Aug 2015
